            <lb/>
3<lb/>
five minutes, the fourth in an hour and<lb/>
forty minutes and the fifth in an hour. I<lb/>
saw a man carrying some meat in the<lb/>
sun at the first post; it was so hot and<lb/>
there were so many flies upon it, that it<lb/>
stood a chance of not only being roasted,<lb/>
but eaten, before he got to the next village<lb/>
