Is not the want of religious instinct in<lb/>
the new Hollanders, a proof that they<lb/>
are a distinct creation, as the Kangaroo<lb/>
and <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag668"
                ref="#misc_732"
                type="miscellaneous">
               <term xml:id="tag668">
          Ornithorinchus Paradoxicus
        </term>
            </rs>.<lb/>
One sees in all this why the Jews were<lb/>
