considered with respect to infinity: and<lb/>
to make infinite wisdom and goodness after<lb/>
our models, is absurd; <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">as much</del> more so<lb/>
