276<lb/>
[horizontal rule]<lb/>
The last work of my Brother<lb/>
                  <rs xml:id="ttag832" ref="#otherwork_047" type="otherwork">
                     <bibl xml:id="tag832">
            "The consolations in Travel"
        </bibl>
                  </rs> or<lb/>
" Last days of a Philosopher"<lb/>
consists of six Dialogues &amp;<lb/>
is of a miscellaneous nature.<lb/>
The first dialogue relates<lb/>
to the progress of society,<lb/>
the advance of science &amp;<lb/>
art &amp; their influence &amp;<lb/>
the influence of various forms<lb/>
of religion on mankind,<lb/>
with speculations on intellect<lb/>
