states of existence in other<lb/>
worlds: - given in the form<lb/>
of a vision, which one of<lb/>
the dramatis personae has<lb/>
                  <del rend="strikethrough">in that</del> by moon light amongst<lb/>
the ruins of the <rs xml:id="ttag833" ref="#place_199" type="place">
                     <name xml:id="tag833" type="place">
          Colisaeum
        </name>
